fields.name: Red Seedless Grapes
fields.description:
Sweet, juicy and crunchy. Red Grapes are full of antioxidants and are a good source of vitamin C and fibre.

A handful of grapes count as one of your 5-a-day.

Storage
Keep refrigerated.

Instructions
Wash before use

Country of Origin
Country of origin may vary due to seasonality.

Country of origin may vary between Brazil, Chile, Egypt, Greece, India, Israel, Italy, Mexico, Morocco, Namibia, Peru, Portugal, Spain, South Africa, USA.
